1.2.0
- Scan directories (application/blocks and package_handle/blocks) for view files that contain:
  - a <form> tag
  - the mail() function
  - ->make('mail')
  - ->make('helper/mail')
Blocks that contain those strings, will be displayed on the Scan > Blocks page.

